    Select variable from a dataframe

    select.Rd

    Selects and prints a specific variable or multiple variables of a dataframe.

    Usage

    select(df, var)

    Arguments

    df

    Dataframe.

    var

    Variable/column name(s) or number(s).

    Value

    Variable(s) selected from provided dataframe.

    Examples
